title: Tavo Erdve
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Buffet, Take-out, European, Lithuanian
description: Your Space restaurant serves vegetarian and vegan food using organic ingredients. Offers daily changing soups from 12-3pm, plus bread with condiments, vegetable cake and other dishes. Also serves soy products, fresh fruit, nutritional cocktails, desserts, coffee, herbal tea, and Indian tea with spices. Hosts lectures and free meditation lessons; vegetarian cooking classes on Saturday. Sells literature and meditation music.
